</taxonomicName>
, by original designation.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BE1212CFFF0682D45CA301ABE53FAC2" blockId="5.[151,1437,1297,1360]" pageId="5" pageNumber="288">
The endemic Australian genus is represented by seven species (
<bibRefCitation id="EFCF5CDDFFF0682D4605301ABE69FAA6" author="Cartwright, D. I." box="[856,1042,1297,1323]" pageId="5" pageNumber="288" pagination="17 - 30" refId="ref14740" refString="Cartwright, D. I. (2011) Descriptions of Neboissomina, new genus and 6 new species of Ecnomidae from Australia (Trichoptera). Zootaxa, 2736 (1), 17 - 30. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 2736.1.2" type="journal article" year="2011">Cartwright 2011</bibRefCitation>
) and to the endemic NT species, 
<taxonomicName id="4C5E5AAFFFF0682D40DE3019BBE0FAC2" authority="Cartwright 2011" authorityName="Cartwright" authorityYear="2011" class="Insecta" family="Ecnomidae" genus="Neboissomina" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trichoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="288" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="riyala">
<emphasis id="B92AFD3EFFF0682D40DE3019BAA1FAC2" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="288">N. riyala</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFCF5CDDFFF0682D45BC303EBBE0FAC2" author="Cartwright, D. I." box="[225,411,1333,1359]" pageId="5" pageNumber="288" pagination="17 - 30" refId="ref14740" refString="Cartwright, D. I. (2011) Descriptions of Neboissomina, new genus and 6 new species of Ecnomidae from Australia (Trichoptera). Zootaxa, 2736 (1), 17 - 30. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 2736.1.2" type="journal article" year="2011">Cartwright 2011</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, we add a second Top End endemic, 
<taxonomicName id="4C5E5AAFFFF0682D4665303DB9BCFAC2" authority="Cartwright &amp; Dostine, 2022" authorityName="Cartwright &amp; Dostine" authorityYear="2022" box="[824,967,1333,1359]" class="Insecta" family="Ecnomidae" genus="Neboissomina" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trichoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="288" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="topendica" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis id="B92AFD3EFFF0682D4665303DB9BCFAC2" box="[824,967,1333,1359]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="288">N. topendica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis id="B92AFD3EFFF0682D4693303EBE53FAC2" bold="true" box="[974,1064,1333,1359]" pageId="5" pageNumber="288">
<taxonomicNameLabel id="A2194045FFF0682D4693303EBE53FAC2" box="[974,1064,1333,1359]" pageId="5" pageNumber="288" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
</paragraph>
